1
00:00:01,626 --> 00:00:02,502
Tell me why.

2
00:00:03,586 --> 00:00:05,338
You already know how it ends.

3
00:00:08,633 --> 00:00:11,052
Well, then, start from the beginning.

4
00:00:16,599 --> 00:00:17,642
The tics.

5
00:00:19,686 --> 00:00:20,562
Ben.

6
00:00:20,645 --> 00:00:21,563
Thoughts.

7
00:00:24,399 --> 00:00:25,567
Impulses.

8
00:00:27,652 --> 00:00:29,571
I managed to suppress them.

9
00:00:31,489 --> 00:00:32,741
Most of the time.

10
00:00:34,534 --> 00:00:35,452
What's going on, Ben?

11
00:00:43,376 --> 00:00:44,461
Wait.

12
00:00:45,128 --> 00:00:46,338
What the hell happened to him?

13
00:00:46,421 --> 00:00:48,256
I beat up some guys in a bar.

14
00:00:50,925 --> 00:00:53,470
And I got plastered.

15
00:01:10,862 --> 00:01:12,155
What are you thinking about over there?

16
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:15,992
A bit of an existential crisis
if I'm honest.

17
00:01:17,118 --> 00:01:18,620
Struck a nerve, huh?

